= jQuery.i18n

jQuery.i18n is a jQuery plugin that makes it easy to internationalize your AJAX applications.



== Usage
    
    
    $.i18n.locale = "en"
    
    $.translations['en'] = {
      hello_world: "Hello World"
    }
    
    $.translations['es'] = {
      hello_world:'Hola Mundo'
    }
    
    $.t('hello_world') // Hello World
    $.i18n.changeLocale('es')s
    
    $.t('hello_world') // Hola Mundo
    




